etch-support (0.02) unstable; urgency=low

  * Temporarily divert debconf-apt-progress in /target and replace it with a
    version that supports new options used in the Lenny installer.

 -- Frans Pop <fjp@debian.org>  Mon, 03 Mar 2008 16:25:53 +0100

etch-support (0.01) unstable; urgency=low

  * First release.
  * Support installation of 'etchnhalf' kernel meta packages.
  * Replace /etc/mke2fs.conf with a version containing defaults compatible
    with Etch.

